{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过实验探究活动，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">找出同种物质的质量与体积的关系，提高对物质属性的认识</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同种物质的质量与体积成正比。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天平、砝码、体积不同的物块、刻度尺</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.提出问题：</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同种物质，体积不同时，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">质量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不相同</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">质量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与体积</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可能存在什么关系呢？</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.猜想和假设：</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同种物质的体积越大时</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，它的质量就越大。同种</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">物质</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的质量与体积可能存在</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正比的关系</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.设计实验和</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进行实验：</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）天平调平后</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，分别测量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">物块的质量记入表格。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）用烧杯</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分别测量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">出它们的体积记入表格。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以体积</span></span><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><em>V</em></span></em><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">横坐标</span></span><span style=\"font-fam